1
00:00:48,460 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:55,580
=Episode 7=

3
00:00:55,799 --> 00:00:56,679
Save her!

4
00:00:58,159 --> 00:00:59,000
If she dies,

5
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,640
you all die!

6
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:03,119
Your Majesty, the wounds are too deep.

7
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,439
There's nothing more we can do.

8
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:05,719
Useless!

9
00:01:05,959 --> 00:01:07,079
Useless bunch!

10
00:01:07,799 --> 00:01:08,760
Get out!

11
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:09,799
Out!

12
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:10,959
Out!

13
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:21,159
Mu Ruyi.

14
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:23,760
I won't allow you to die.

15
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:26,400
Your life belongs to me.

16
00:01:26,959 --> 00:01:28,200
In this life,

17
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:31,079
the next,

18
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:34,959
and forever,

19
00:01:36,599 --> 00:01:38,519
I will carry this hatred to my grave.

20
00:01:42,439 --> 00:01:46,799
I never want to see you again.

21
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:57,280
Mu Ruyi.

22
00:01:58,840 --> 00:01:59,519
Mu Ruyi.

23
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,239
Mu Ruyi.

24
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,640
Don't die!

25
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:06,359
Mu Ruyi!

26
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:13,840
Wake up!

27
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:55,800
Mu Ruyi.

28
00:02:58,599 --> 00:03:01,000
I've imagined a thousand ways
this could end,

29
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,240
but I never expected

30
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,560
you'd choose this one.

31
00:03:45,199 --> 00:03:45,879
Who are you?

32
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,840
I saved you. Stop yelling.

33
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,080
Spare the slick talk.

34
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:51,919
Who exactly are you?

35
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:52,919
Heroic lady,

36
00:03:53,879 --> 00:03:54,759
my name is Mo Shuo.

37
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:55,840
I'm a military physician.

38
00:03:56,439 --> 00:03:57,400
We've met before.

39
00:03:57,599 --> 00:03:58,400
(Command)
Don't you remember?

40
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,400
In the stinky tofu shop?

41
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,840
Mr. Stinky Tofu!

42
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,919
I happened to be passing by
and saved you.

43
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,360
I've already introduced myself.

44
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,959
May I ask your name?

45
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:18,160
What do you do?

46
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:21,240
I met you
on the road to the capital yesterday.

47
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,519
Are you part of the royal house?

48
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,519
My name is Xia Ke'er.

49
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,120
I'm no heroine,

50
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:29,079
just a countrywoman.

51
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:32,160
My sister runs a stall

52
00:04:32,319 --> 00:04:33,360
at the market in the capital.

53
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:36,240
She hasn't come home for days.

54
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,319
I was on my way searching for her

55
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,680
when I ran into those thugs.

56
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,360
Thank you for saving me, sir.

57
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:43,639
I see.

58
00:04:48,439 --> 00:04:50,319
I'm truly worried about her,

59
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:53,360
so I got a fake pass

60
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:55,360
to slip into the capital and find her.

61
00:04:56,079 --> 00:04:57,160
Put that away.

62
00:04:57,279 --> 00:04:58,160
Don't let anyone see it.

63
00:04:59,079 --> 00:05:00,920
I'll keep your secret. Don't worry.

64
00:05:02,759 --> 00:05:04,759
Then let me treat you
to stinky tofu rice noodles!

65
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:05,639
Sure.

66
00:05:10,639 --> 00:05:12,120
(One Month Later)
General Xia must have a secret ally.

67
00:05:12,399 --> 00:05:13,600
(One Month Later)
We've found no trace of her yet.

68
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:18,680
She must have been the one
who tried to kill me.

69
00:05:19,079 --> 00:05:20,040
Investigate further. Dig deeper.

70
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:20,720
Yes.

71
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,360
About that woman...

72
00:05:25,199 --> 00:05:25,879
Any news?

73
00:05:26,399 --> 00:05:28,120
Your Majesty, I have failed you.

74
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:30,319
We've selected so many consorts,

75
00:05:30,839 --> 00:05:32,120
but still cannot find one
who looks like the Princess,

76
00:05:32,759 --> 00:05:33,240
sorry,

77
00:05:33,439 --> 00:05:35,680
looks like Mu Riyi.

78
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,439
Keep searching.

79
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,959
Your Majesty is truly
a man of deep devotion.

80
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,399
Ever since Mu Ruyi's death,

81
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,839
you've been in low spirits.

82
00:05:45,439 --> 00:05:48,600
You might find some distraction
at the music house.

83
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:53,360
Cheap and common women.

84
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,319
Never bring me to such places again.

85
00:05:55,399 --> 00:05:55,839
Yes.

86
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:30,959
Mu Ruyi?

87
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,959
You must have the wrong person, sir.

88
00:06:40,399 --> 00:06:42,079
My name is Jing Liuli.

89
00:06:42,519 --> 00:06:43,839
I've been alone since I was a child.

90
00:06:44,279 --> 00:06:45,399
My life has been adrift.

91
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:48,360
I came here to perform
because I had no other choice.

92
00:06:50,439 --> 00:06:50,959
Sir!

93
00:06:51,399 --> 00:06:52,639
You truly don't remember me?

94
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,560
Please show some respect, sir.

95
00:06:59,279 --> 00:07:00,480
You're really not her?

96
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,160
What do you want?

97
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,439
I'll pay for your time tonight.

98
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,279
You belong to me now.

99
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,720
I can take you wherever I please.

100
00:07:24,279 --> 00:07:25,879
I'm paid to perform, not to date.

101
00:07:26,079 --> 00:07:27,279
If you persist in this misconduct,

102
00:07:27,399 --> 00:07:28,439
I will call the officials.

103
00:07:40,519 --> 00:07:41,360
What are you doing?

104
00:07:41,839 --> 00:07:42,839
You should knock before entering.

105
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,199
How did you get hurt?

106
00:07:52,639 --> 00:07:55,439
I fell into a river.

107
00:07:56,439 --> 00:07:58,600
How could that leave wounds like this?

108
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,600
Where have you actually been?

109
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,199
Those brutal Dongqing soldiers

110
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,759
butchered my family.

111
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:11,480
They say people in Dongqing
are treacherous.

112
00:08:11,879 --> 00:08:13,600
They leave no survivors
wherever they go.

113
00:08:13,959 --> 00:08:15,199
How's your family?

114
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:16,920
If they do survive,

115
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,399
I can ask someone to help.

116
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:24,560
It's too late.

117
00:08:25,959 --> 00:08:26,839
My family

118
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,000
and my best friends

119
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:32,840
fell at the hands of Dongqing.

120
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:40,240
Are you really just a countrywoman?

121
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,399
No more questions.

122
00:08:44,799 --> 00:08:45,519
Leave!

123
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:46,960
Why are you still here?

124
00:08:47,559 --> 00:08:48,639
Want to try my blade?

125
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,519
Leave!

126
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:51,000
You're hurt.

127
00:08:51,879 --> 00:08:52,919
It's not easy on your own.

128
00:08:53,759 --> 00:08:54,960
I can't just leave you alone.

129
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,080
Don't read too much into it.

130
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,720
Just consider it
a physician's compassion.

131
00:09:13,039 --> 00:09:13,759
(In recent years,)

132
00:09:14,559 --> 00:09:16,679
(the war between Xiling and Dongqing
has never ceased.)

133
00:09:17,279 --> 00:09:19,000
(If I meet with misfortune one day,)

134
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:21,840
(I'll fake my death with this pill.)

135
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:23,879
(Make sure you get the timing right)

136
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,559
(and wait for me
outside the royal mausoleum.)

137
00:09:38,399 --> 00:09:39,080
Ling Xiao.

138
00:09:39,759 --> 00:09:40,519
I told you,

139
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,639
even if I die,

140
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,840
I will never let you go.
